OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 28 Jun to Tue 7 Jul
OL,6,FFairly changeable conditions at first
OL,7,Fwith periods of rain and showers, and
OL,8,Fthere could be some thundery outbreaks
OL,9,Fat times. Perhaps a drier start to
OL,10,FJuly for many, although the northwest
OL,11,Fmay still see some rain at times, and
OL,12,Fperhaps accompanied by some strong
OL,13,Fwinds. Temperatures remain widely
OL,14,Fabove average, and there remains a
OL,15,Fchance of some very warm or hot
OL,16,Fweather returning, mainly across the
OL,17,Fsouth.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
